data.description: Beautiful rancher in desirable Brookeville, Olney Mill neighborhood. Updates include - 40-year Landmark Pro asphalt shingles r/oof in Jan. 2017, HVAC unit replaced in Oct. 2019,. Granite countertops,  SS appliances & ceramic floor in Kitchen.  Kitchen has been opened up with an arched doorway to living room with large bay window overlooking landscaped front yard.  3 bedrooms and 2 updated full bathrooms. Primary bath with jetted tub.  Entire home freshly painted. Entire lower level flooring replaced in 2019 with Lifeproof High traffic Vinyl, (scratch proof), Family room has a  wood burning fireplace, sliding glass door to enormous back yard, playground set and even a trampoline.  Separate Laundry room and storage area,  another full bathroom and huge open "flex" room, whether you need space for play room/office/extra bedroom/movie theater...  1 block from pool and playground.
